{"tid":2311993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國係月球表面扯旗","createTime":"2020-12-04T13:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T13:21:25.000Z","uid":162874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4465aa0cf07dff903c464fc7976dbed84a0d6ba","tid":2311993,"uid":162874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"航天科工集團航天三江九部研製團隊表示，月球的環境會令普通旗幟在短時間內褪色甚至分解，故其為了是次的月面國旗展開進行了一段長時間的研究，只在選材上已花費超過 1 年，再通過熱匹配性、耐高低溫、防靜電、防月球塵埃等試驗，才選定某新型複合材料，製成了嫦娥五號展示的國旗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpK3red.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpK3red.png&h=a527939d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美帝：Am I a joke to you?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGKOCkS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGKOCkS.jpg&h=2409139f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fac4a8fb481d9f0785a74d7e50f14cf9902771e","tid":2311993,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae7dc5b4e7ea2e650125b05560a3409de3034f0b","tid":2311993,"uid":162874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/04/change-5-3/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR0By44NRm_0QMNQYTiBy9dVQId-LU4CnM-kK4oBCHcS6LvxDGAnvFI9PBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F04%2Fchange-5-3%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0By44NRm_0QMNQYTiBy9dVQId-LU4CnM-kK4oBCHcS6LvxDGAnvFI9PBQ&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=96606141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/04/change-5-3/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR0By44NRm_0QMNQYTiBy9dVQId-LU4CnM-kK4oBCHcS6LvxDGAnvFI9PBQ</a>"},{"pid":"90ad085384cd5764575d9325376a4524b4588c95","tid":2311993,"uid":214679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"呢次自主研發使咗幾多錢"}]}